                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿فَٱرۡتَقِبۡ﴾: فانْتَظِرْ.</h2>\n<p>﴿بِدُخَانٖ﴾: ظُلْمَةٍ كَهَيئَةِ الدُّخانِ بِسَبَبِ الجَدْبِ.</p>\n<h2>﴿مُبِينٖ﴾: واضِحٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "44:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿يَغۡشَى﴾: يَعُمُّ.</h2>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "44:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>...</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "44:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أَنَّىٰ﴾: كَيفَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰ﴾: التَّذَكُّرُ والاتِّعاظُ.</h2>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "44:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿تَوَلَّوۡاْ عَنۡهُ﴾: أَعْرَضُوا عَنْه.</h2>\n<h2>﴿مُعَلَّمٞ﴾: عَلَّمَه بَشَرٌ أو الكَهَنَةُ أو الشَّياطِينُ.</h2>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "44:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>...</p>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "44:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿نَبۡطِشُ﴾: نُعَذِّبُ، والبَطْشُ أَخْذٌ بِشِدَّةٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "44:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿فَتَنَّا﴾: ابْتَلينا واخْتَبَرْنا.</h2>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "44:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿أَدُّوٓاْ﴾: سَلِّمُوا وأرْسِلُوا مَعِي.</h2>\n<h2>﴿عِبَادَ ٱللَّهِ﴾: بَنِي إسْرائِيلَ.</h2>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "44:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿وَأَن لَّا تَعۡلُواْ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ﴾: لا تَتَكَبَّرُوا على اللهِ بِتَكْذِيبِ رُسُلِه.</p>\n<h2>﴿بِسُلۡطَٰنٖ﴾: بِبُرْهانٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "44:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿عُذۡتُ بِرَبِّي﴾: استَجَرْتُ بِاللهِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿تَرۡجُمُونِ﴾: تَقْتُلُوني رَجْماً بالحِجارَةِ.</h2>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "44:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿فَٱعۡتَزِلُونِ﴾: كُفُّوا عَنْ أذَايَ.</h2>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "44:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مُجۡرِمُونَ﴾: مُشْرِكُونَ بِاللهِ كافِرُونَ.</h2>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "44:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿فَأَسۡرِ﴾: اجْعَلْهُم يَسِيُرونَ لَيلاً.</h2>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "44:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿رَهۡوًا﴾: سَاكِناً مُسْتَقِرّاً عَلَى حالِه مُنْفَرِجاً.</h2>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "44:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>...</p>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "44:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَمَقَامٖ كَرِيمٖ﴾: وَمَنازِلَ جَمِيلَةٍ.</h2>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "44:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَنَعۡمَةٖ﴾: عَيْشٍ لَيِّنٍ رَغْدٍ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿فَٰكِهِينَ﴾: مُتَنَعِّمِينَ، مُتْرَفِينَ.</h2>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "44:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿كَذَٰلِكَ﴾: مِثْلَ ذَلِكَ العِقابِ يُعاقِبُ اللهُ مَنْ كَذَّبَ وَبَدّلَ نِعْمةَ اللهِ كُفْراً.</p>\n<h2>﴿وَأَوۡرَثۡنَٰهَا﴾: ومَلَّكْناها.</h2>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "44:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مُنظَرِينَ﴾: مُؤَخَّرِينَ عَنِ العُقُوبَةِ.</h2>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "44:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ٱلۡمُهِينِ﴾: المُذِلِّ.</h2>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "44:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿عَالِيٗا﴾: جَبَّاراً.</h2>\n<p>﴿مِنَ ٱلۡمُسۡرِفِينَ﴾: مُتَجاوِزاً للحَدِّ في العُلوِّ والتَّكَبُّرِ عَلَى عبادِ اللهِ.</p>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "44:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ﴾: عالَمِي زَمانِهِم.</h2>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
                "44:33": {
                    "id": 33
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ٱلۡأٓيَٰتِ﴾: المُعْجِزاتِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿بَلَٰٓؤٞاْ﴾: اخْتِبارٌ بالرَّخاءِ والشِّدَةِ.</h2>"
        },
